<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>h6</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>h6</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br></div></div><p>**es una mala practica no usar de forma correcta las etiquetas de encabezado **.</p>
