<div class="language-html ext-html line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-html"><code><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>span</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>Details<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><h2 id="etiqueta-nav" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#etiqueta-nav" aria-hidden="true">#</a> etiqueta nav</h2>
